title: Episode 365: The Late Bloomer (Feat. Bill Bellamy)
itunes:title: Episode 365: The Late Bloomer (Feat. Bill Bellamy)
description:
Comedian/Actor, Bill Bellamy joins the ladies of Lip Service this week to promote his latest stand up special "I Want My Life Back." Bill breaks down why women are better players than men, why he was so protective of his image during his MTV days, inventing the term 'booty call,' and much more. Enjoy!
